Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:13.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:26.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:30.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:33.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:02.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:13.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:15.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:19.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,120.389)}The Monstrous Semiminga's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}Song of Slaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I got another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You got another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki,\Nyou're a master cicada-catcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll get one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission\Nto take these cicadas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This forest belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your cicadas, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cicadas these days can\Nfetch a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those stupid children...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My head's splitting in two...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my net.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll wait here.\N- Hurry up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid cicadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish human...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll become a guinea\Npig for Semiminga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounded like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment was\Na roaring success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes for\Nyour deadly sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can escape my\Nkiller sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll murder everyone in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See that it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sighted children in the forest\Nwhere Semiminga did his tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even children can be spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Semiminga, go finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so creeped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't leave Naoki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all\Ncarry him together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You left your net on\Nthe path back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cicada monster...\NIt was a cicada monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get him home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get his hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi has the child...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... just you watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Approaching attack target.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world did Naoki see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He insists it was\Na cicada monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A cicada monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A cicada, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a Shocker\Ncyborg, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it might just be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing him to your\Napartment means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's Shocker,\Nthey'll strike soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And when that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Change direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, initiate attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cicada's cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki,\Nget Naoki out of here at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer sound waves\Nmust have killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Search carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I the one you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer sound waves, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That might kill\Na normal human...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But they won't be\Nenough to hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the killer sound\Nwaves transmitted from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Emergency order.\NEmergency order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pursuer detected.\NPursuer detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The transmitter for the sound\Nwaves must be under that canopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo is up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki? Where's Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him out safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,\Ntry to get the driver for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,, - Hongo!\N- Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer sound waves came\Nfrom inside this truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's see what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one producing\Nthe killer sound waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you this long\Nto realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's killer sound waves come from\Nme, Semiminga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you\Nget away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly, Semiminga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The world around me...\Ngoing dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider,\NI'll finish you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,by sucking out all your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:43.36,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an7\c&H000000&\2c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Ishiyama General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi has likely been\Nhospitalized with serious injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:06.04,Italics,,0,0,0,,Good. Keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mortal enemy, Hongo Takeshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,has been paralyzed from the waist down\Nby Semiminga's killer sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now nobody will be\Nable to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can turn Tokyo into\Na land of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The unexplained deaths\Nin Tokyo caused by the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,killer sound waves\Nwill inspire a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to secure\Na broadcast tower for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's easily done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see what\NAmbassador Hell can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See that you succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Semiminga, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Occupy the broadcast tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're watching us like hawks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For Heaven's sake.\NDon't scare me like that, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When Taki called,\NI thought they'd gotten you for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\Nit wasn't entirely a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If he'd come any later, that cicada\Nwould have fried my brain for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're all right, why not walk out\Ninstead of checking into the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shocker thinks I'm paralyzed,\Nthey're more likely to let something slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To make best use of\NSemiminga's killer sound waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll want to secure a\Nhigh, unimpeded location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll probably want a\Nbroadcast tower, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... a Shocker Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we need to find\Nthe Shocker Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared a sound\Nwave detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'd better call Emi\Ntoo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What's the word?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Never said finding Shocker\NTower would be easy, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start complaining yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a long way to\Ngo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, something's off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But... in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry! Hurry!\N- Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- C'mon.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No visitors allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We were out hiking, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us have lunch, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We promise we won't\Nget in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll eat fast and\Nbe out of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be long, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That went perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That broadcast tower must be the\NShocker Tower that Takeshi mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's contact him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki? Hongo? Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you'll come with me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you contact Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency call from\NAmbassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo and Taki have\Nvanished from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to broadcast\Nthe killer sound waves ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Hongo and Taki must\Nhave followed them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch me now...\NI'll smoke you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're hiding nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better show yourself\Nbefore I count to five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't,\NI'll kill all your comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to let your comrades die\Nfor fear of my killer sound waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have to kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just them....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bathe Tokyo in my killer sound\Nwaves from here in Shocker Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Semiminga...\Nsorry to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but we have an electric\Ncurrent blocking your
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,killer sound waves running\Nall around this tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so busy\Nsearching for me and Taki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't even notice what\Nwas going on around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that brat Taki set\Nup the jamming current?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This will protect the tower\Nfrom the killer sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take care of\NPops and the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:56.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:59.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.17,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:06.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:10.19,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:14.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:20.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:25.10,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:28.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:39.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:43.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:46.47,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:50.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:53.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:57.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:08.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:11.33,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:22.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:25.84,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:29.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:33.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:36.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:40.40,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.73,0:22:43.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:51.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:54.74,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't\Nreach all of Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,my power can still kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!\NI won't rest until I defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider,\Nleave the small fry to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting, Semiminga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He beat the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hadn't made it in time,\NJapan would've been in serious trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:00.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's killer sound\Nwaves plan was foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker was already\Npreparing its next cyborg foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:05.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:08.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.97,Cont,,0,70,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:13.14,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:16.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:17.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Kabutrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kabutrong is ordered\Nto turn the children
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:23.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,of the world into\NShocker combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:28.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Monstrous\NDoctor Insect and the Shocker School."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:31.11,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs113\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(477.167,730.389)}The Monstrous Doctor Insect\Nand the Shocker School
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:41.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:45.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:48.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:50.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:52.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:56.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:58.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:04.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:07.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:11.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:15.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Semiminga's\NSong of Slaughter!
Comment: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Doctor Insect\Nand the Shocker School